---
title: BBQ Pork Ribs with Cheesy Mash and Kale Salad
description: Rib dinner in 35 minutes?!? Layers of creamy, cheesy potatoes get topped with fall-off-the-bone BBQ-glazed ribs and a kale salad with sweet apricot dressing. Simple, convenient and delicious!
